{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}噢 几个孩子
Oh, they're kids.

315
00:18:00,490 --> 00:18:01,870
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你们是警察吗
Are you the police?

316
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:06,020
