{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}什么都不要动
Don't touch anything!

330
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:56,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}把鞋给我
Give me your shoe.

331
00:20:18,390 --> 00:20:20,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那是车钥匙吗
Were those the car keys?

332
