{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我看不出来
I see nothing.

349
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:14,090
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}也许它并不是你追求的那种美
Or perhaps that is not the beauty you seek.

350
00:24:20,010 --> 00:24:20,790
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她怎么样了
How is she?

351
00:24:21,470 --> 00:24:23,350
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你的人类女友很聪明
She's quite clever, your mortal.

352
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:24,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}尽管她还不了解天体聚合
She doesn't know it yet,

353
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,720
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}但她正在进行研究
but she studies the Convergence as well.

354
00:24:27,620 --> 00:24:28,320
