{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她不见了
I can't see her.

357
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:17,640
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}简
Jane!

358
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,440
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你到底去哪儿了
Where the hell were you?

359
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:22,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}别告诉我你已经报警了
Tell me you didn't call the police!

360
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:23,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那我还能干什么
What was I supposed to do?

361
00:25:23,250 --> 00:25:24,320
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不应该报警
Not call the police!

362
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你吓坏我了
I was freaking out.

363
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,680
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你报警 就会惊动政府
You call the cops, they tell the Feds,

364
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:28,490
