{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你说过你会回来
You said you were coming back.

384
00:26:33,860 --> 00:26:36,820
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}知道 知道 可是彩虹桥被破坏了
I know, I know, but the Bifrost was destroyed.

385
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:38,570
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}要知道九大国度乱作一团
The Nine Realms erupted into chaos,

386
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:41,050
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}烽烟四起 掠夺者趁火打劫
wars were raging, marauders were pillaging.

387
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:43,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我必须先结束动乱
I had to put an end to the slaughter.

388
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:48,040
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果真是这样 那还说得过去
As excuses go, it's not terrible.

389
00:26:48,450 --> 00:26:51,670
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可我在电视上看到你了 你 你在纽约
But I saw you on TV, you were...you were in New York!

390
