{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}把你的手放在头上 往后退
Place your hands on your heads, step back!

422
00:28:10,570 --> 00:28:11,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这位女士身体不适
This woman is unwell.

423
00:28:11,890 --> 00:28:13,060
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她很危险
She's dangerous.

424
