She's ill.

444
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,770
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她是凡人
She is mortal.

445
00:30:43,630 --> 00:30:45,360
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}凡人当然会生病
Illness is their defining trait.

446
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:47,060
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我带她来 是因为我们可以帮她
I brought her here because we can help her.

447
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:49,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她不能进我们阿萨神域的殿堂
She does not belong here in Asgard

448
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:52,610
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}就像有些菜不能上台面一样
anymore than a goat belongs at a banquet table.

449
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:53,980
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他怎么
Did he just...?

450
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:56,260
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你以为你是谁啊
Who do you think you are?

451
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:58,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我是奥丁 众神之王
I'm Odin. King of Asgard.

452
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,920
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}九大国度的保护者
Protector of the Nine Realms.

453
00:31:02,740 --> 00:31:03,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}哦 我
Oh. Well, I'm...

454
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:06,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我知道你是谁 简·福斯特
I know very well who you are, Jane Foster.

455
00:31:07,270 --> 00:31:08,820
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你跟你父亲说过我
You told your dad about me?

456
00:31:09,550 --> 00:31:10,960
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她体内存在某种物质 父王
Something is within her, father,

457
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,110
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我从未见过的物质
something I have not seen before.

458
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:14,650
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}人类世界有自己的治疗师 叫医生
Her world has its healers. They are called "doctors."

459
00:31:14,650 --> 00:31:15,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}让医生处理吧
Let them deal with it.

460
00:31:15,910 --> 00:31:17,750
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}卫兵 马上送她回地球
Guards, take her back to Midgard.

461
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,480
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不 别
No, I wouldn't...

462
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:23,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}碰她
...touch her.

463
00:31:23,980 --> 00:31:25,190
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}简 你没事吧
Jane, are you alright?

464
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,280
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这不可能
It's impossible.

465
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:35,390
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她体内的物质 在保护她
The infection, it's defending her.

466
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,270
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不
No,

467
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它在保护自己
it's defending itself.

468
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:42,050
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}跟我来
Come with me.

469
00:31:42,820 --> 00:31:46,390
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}有一些宇宙形成前残留的物质
There are relics that predate the universe itself.

470
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:50,530
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}她体内的东西 似乎是其中的一种
What lies within her appears to be one of them.

471
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:53,760
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}九大国度并非一成不变
The Nine Realms are not eternal.

472
00:31:54,410 --> 00:31:56,990
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它们有黎明 当然也有黄昏
They had a dawn as they will have a dusk.

473
00:31:58,100 --> 00:32:00,430
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}在黎明之前 黑暗势力
But before that dawn the dark forces,

474
00:32:00,430 --> 00:32:04,220
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}也就是黑暗精灵 一统天下
the Dark Elves, reigned absolute

475
00:32:04,220 --> 00:32:05,930
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}独霸一方
and unchallenged.

476
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}起源于无边黑暗的
"Born of eternal night,

477
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:11,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}黑暗精灵要把光偷走
the Dark Elves comes to steal away your light."

478
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:15,110
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我知道那些故事 小时候妈妈给我讲过
They were these stories mother told them to us as children.

479
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,220
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他们的首领 玛勒基斯
Their leader, Malekith

480
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}利用黑暗制造了一种武器
made a weapon out of that darkness,

481
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:20,730
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}叫做以太
and it was called the Aether.

482
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:23,760
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}其它的残留物通常很像石头
While the other relics often appeared as stones,

483
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:26,660
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}但以太是液体 并且不断变化
the Aether is fluid and everchanging.

484
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:29,110
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它把各种物质转化成黑暗物质
It changes matter into dark matter,

485
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,350
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它寻找寄居的宿主
it seeks out to host bodies,

486
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:33,870
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}从宿主的生命力中吸取能量
drawing strength from their life force.

487
00:32:34,250 --> 00:32:37,320
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯企图通过以太的力量
Malekith sought to use the Aether's power

488
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:41,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}使宇宙重新回归黑暗
to return the universe to one of darkness.

489
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:44,630
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}但是 经过不屈不挠的浴血奋战
But after eternities of blood shed,

490
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:47,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我的父王波尔 最终获得胜利
my father Bor, finally triumphed,

491
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:52,210
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}因此赢得了持续数千年的和平
ushering in the peace that lasted thousands of years.

492
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:54,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他怎么取胜的
What happened?

493
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他消灭了他们
He killed them all.

494
00:32:57,390 --> 00:32:58,780
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你肯定吗
Are you certain?

495
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}据说以太也同时被消灭了
The Aether was said to have been destroyed with them

496
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:03,020
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可如今再度献身
and yet here it is.

497
00:33:04,390 --> 00:33:06,320
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}黑暗精灵的确消亡了
The Dark Elves are dead.

498
00:33:07,610 --> 00:33:10,140
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你的书中有没有提到 怎么排出它们
Does your book happen to mention how to get it out of me?

499
00:33:11,010 --> 00:33:14,430
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}没有 没有涉及
No, it does not.

500
00:34:38,390 --> 00:34:41,320
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}让我们负责看管俘虏 未免太大材小用了
Acting as caretakers to these scoundrels is beneath us.

501
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:42,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}噢 没错
Oh, please.

502
00:34:42,750 --> 00:34:44,800
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你的身材的确够大 我的朋友
If they were beneath you my rotund friend,

503
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,000
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}能把人压死
they'd all be dead.

504
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:01,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}排好队
Keep in line.

505
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:03,110
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}走快点
Move it!

506
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:06,920
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}奥丁不断地为我提供新的朋友
Odin continues to bring me new friends.

507
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,900
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}真的很体贴
How thoughtful.

508
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:12,630
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我送来的书你不感兴趣是吗
The books I sent, do they not interest you?

509
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:17,500
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你想让我后半辈子当书虫吗 读书
Is that how I'm to wile away eternity, reading?

510
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:20,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我已经竭尽全力让你过得舒适一些了 洛基
I've done everything in my power to make you comfortable, Loki.

511
00:35:20,740 --> 00:35:21,860
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}是吗
Have you?

512
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:24,830
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}奥丁是否也这么想
Does Odin share your concern?

513
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,420
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}还有索尔
Does Thor?

514
00:35:27,810 --> 00:35:31,400
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}让他们日夜为我操心 我还真有点过意不去
It must be so inconvenient them asking after me day and night.

515
00:35:31,410 --> 00:35:34,940
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你走到今天这一步 完全都是你咎由自取
You know full well it was your actions that brought you here.

516
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:36,280
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}咎由自取
My actions.

517
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:38,230
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我只不过是揭穿了那个
I was merely giving truth to the lie

518
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:40,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}欺骗了我一生的谎言而已
that I've been fed my entire life,

519
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,810
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}说什么我生而为王
that I was born to be a king.

520
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,850
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}当国王
A king?

521
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:45,870
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}真正的国王勇于承认错误
A true king admits his faults.

522
00:35:45,870 --> 00:35:47,410
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你在地球上残害了多少生命
What of the lives you took on Earth?

523
00:35:47,410 --> 00:35:50,680
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}跟伟大的奥丁杀的人相比 那点人根本不值一提
A mere handful compared to the number Odin has taken himself.

524
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:51,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你父亲
Your father...

525
00:35:51,890 --> 00:35:53,650
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他不是我的父亲
He's not my father!

526
00:35:56,700 --> 00:35:58,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我也不是你母亲吗
Then am I not your mother?

527
00:36:03,970 --> 00:36:05,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你也不是
You're not.

528
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:14,700
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}除了你自己 你好像已经把所有的人都看透了
You're always so perceptive about everyone but yourself.

529
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:32,440
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你去地球找我 是因为我遇到了麻烦
When you came for me, you knew I was in trouble.

530
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:36,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}海姆达尔看不到你了 你不在地球上
When Heimdall had lost sight of you, you were no longer on Earth.

531
00:36:36,420 --> 00:36:37,910
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那怎么可能呢
Well, how's that possible?

532
00:36:37,910 --> 00:36:39,780
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我认为你在 可你不在
I believe you were and you weren't.

533
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:42,490
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}九大国度运行于宇宙生命之树
The Nine Realms travel within Yggdrasil,

534
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:46,080
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它们围绕中庭旋转 犹如地球围绕太阳
orbiting Midgard in much the way your planet orbits the sun.

535
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:50,630
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}每过五千年 它们就会呈直线排列
And every five thousand years the worlds align perfectly,

536
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:52,450
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们称之为天体聚合
and we call this the Convergence.

537
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:58,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}在这段时间 各国边界会出现混淆
During this time the boarders between worlds become blurred.

538
00:36:59,540 --> 00:37:01,880
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可能你已经发现了一些端倪
It's possible you found one of these points.

539
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:06,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}幸好这情况还会改变
We are lucky that it remained open.

540
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:10,030
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}天体聚合过后 直列现象结束
Once the worlds pass out of alignment,

541
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:14,210
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}混淆情况就会消失
the connection is lost.

542
00:37:27,270 --> 00:37:29,730
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我非常喜欢你的表述方式
I liked the way you explained things.

543
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:33,260
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我会有什么事吗
What's gonna happen to me?

544
00:37:33,450 --> 00:37:34,960
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我会想办法救你 简
I'll find a way to save you, Jane.

545
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你父王说 根本
Your father said there was...

546
00:37:36,010 --> 00:37:38,420
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我父王并非无所不知
My father doesn't know everything.

547
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:40,670
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这话可别让他听到
Don't let him hear you say that.

548
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:44,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}简·福斯特 请拜见弗丽嘉
Jane Foster, please meet Frigga,

549
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:46,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}阿萨神域王后 我母亲
Queen of Asgard, my mother.

550
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:49,390
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你好
Hi.

551
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:40,760
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}快
Move!

552
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,560
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}都去地牢
To the dungeons!

553
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:30,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}快点
Come on!

554
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:56,600
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我觉得你应该走左侧的楼梯
You might want to take the stairs to the left.

555
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:08,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}监狱出事了
The prisons.

556
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:09,840
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}洛基
Loki.

557
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:12,220
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}去吧 我会照顾好她
Go, I will look after her.

558
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}看来他们坐牢久了有点情绪
It is as if they resented being imprisoned.

559
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:32,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}有些家伙就是不识好歹
There's no pleasing some creatures.

560
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:42,840
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}现在只要回到牢房 概不追究责任
Return to your cells, no further harm will come to you.

561
00:40:42,850 --> 00:40:44,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我向你们保证
You have my word.

562
00:40:45,900 --> 00:40:48,400
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}非常好 那我就不用客气了
Very well, you do not have my word.

563
00:40:58,230 --> 00:41:00,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}现在马上派人去武器库
Send a squadron to the weapons vault,

564
00:41:00,330 --> 00:41:03,260
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不惜一切代价守住 确保地牢安全
defend it at all costs. Secure the dungeon.

565
00:41:03,270 --> 00:41:04,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}奥丁
Odin.

566
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,370
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}弗丽嘉
Frigga.

567
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:06,540
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}快
Go!

568
00:41:07,570 --> 00:41:09,790
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}小事一桩 不必多虑
It's a skirmish, nothing to fear.

569
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:11,790
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你从来都不会撒谎
You've never been a very good liar.

570
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:14,980
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}带她去你的寝宫 事态平息了我去找你
Take her to you chambers, I'll come for you when it's safe.

571
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:16,670
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}多保重
You take care.

572
00:41:17,050 --> 00:41:18,930
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}经历过那么多风风雨雨
Despite all I have survived,

573
00:41:19,060 --> 00:41:21,640
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我的王后对我还是一往情深
my queen still worries over me.

574
00:41:22,090 --> 00:41:25,130
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}因为我对你一往情深 才能让你逢凶化吉
It's only because I worry over you that you have survived.

575
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:28,770
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}现在你听好了
Listen to me now,

576
00:41:28,870 --> 00:41:32,060
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}无论我说什么你都要照办 不得违抗
I need you to do everything I ask and no questions.

577
00:41:32,290 --> 00:41:33,360
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}遵命 夫人
Yes, ma'am.

578
00:46:42,760 --> 00:46:46,090
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}国王王位被毁坏了 快去保护国王
The throne of Asgard is destroyed! To the king!

579
00:47:01,600 --> 00:47:02,780
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}弗丽嘉
Frigga.

580
00:47:11,520 --> 00:47:13,440
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}别再往前走了
Stand down, creature.

581
00:47:14,060 --> 00:47:15,840
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我可以饶你不死
And you may still survive this.

582
00:47:15,840 --> 00:47:18,050
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你可奈何不了我 女人
I have survive worse, woman.

583
00:47:19,310 --> 00:47:20,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你是谁
Who are you?

584
00:47:21,240 --> 00:47:22,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我是玛勒基斯
I am Malekith.

585
00:47:23,450 --> 00:47:25,520
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}来取回属于我的东西
And I would have what is mine.

586
00:47:56,700 --> 00:47:59,200
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你拿了我的东西 孩子
You have taken something, child.

587
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:01,740
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}还给我
Give it back.

588
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:16,780
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你这巫婆
Witch.

589
00:48:20,230 --> 00:48:21,440
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}以太在哪儿
Where is the Aether.

590
00:48:21,990 --> 00:48:23,840
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不会告诉你
I'll never tell you.

591
00:48:25,090 --> 00:48:26,410
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这我相信
I believe you.

592
00:48:29,320 --> 00:48:31,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不
No.

593
00:51:57,630 --> 00:52:00,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}宇宙运行以五千年为一个周期
The universe rotates on a five thousand years cycle.

594
00:52:00,840 --> 00:52:03,600
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}每个周期 都会出现直列现象
And once a cycle, all the worlds align.

595
00:52:03,770 --> 00:52:06,460
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你们 想象一下这是我们的星球
Imagine... imagine that this is our world,

596
00:52:07,410 --> 00:52:08,200
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}呃 谢谢
oh, thank you,

597
00:52:08,200 --> 00:52:09,610
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这是另一个星球
and this is another world,

598
00:52:09,610 --> 00:52:11,330
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}通常 它们是分开的
normally, they're seperate.

599
00:52:11,680 --> 00:52:13,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可是直列期间
But during the Alignment,

600
00:52:13,550 --> 00:52:15,130
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}整个宇宙互相连接
everything is connected,

601
00:52:15,810 --> 00:52:19,640
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}包括九大国度 九大国度会互相穿行
all nine realms. All nine realms are passing through each other,

602
00:52:19,640 --> 00:52:22,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}重力 光线 甚至物质
and gravity, light, and even matter

603
00:52:22,120 --> 00:52:24,460
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}都会彼此碰撞 混合
is crushing from one world to the other.

604
00:52:26,940 --> 00:52:30,400
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果我们发生这种情况 结果将是毁灭性的
But if this happens to us now, the result could be cataclysmic.

605
00:52:31,190 --> 00:52:33,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我发明的尖峰重力测试仪
My gravimetric-spikes can stablize

606
00:52:33,560 --> 00:52:36,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}能够稳定天体聚合焦点
the focus point of the Convergance.

607
00:52:36,190 --> 00:52:38,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这样一来 九大国度
This time, the Alignment

608
00:52:38,560 --> 00:52:41,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}和其它星体队列就不会碰到我们
and all the other worlds would just pass us by.

609
00:52:41,690 --> 00:52:43,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它很完美
It's beautiful.

610
00:52:44,710 --> 00:52:45,950
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}也很简单
Simple.

611
00:52:45,950 --> 00:52:47,290
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}有问题吗
Any questions?

612
00:52:50,640 --> 00:52:53,730
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}是的 能把鞋还我吗
Yeah, can I have my shoe back?

613
00:53:46,250 --> 00:53:47,850
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}简·福斯特
Jane Foster?

614
00:53:48,720 --> 00:53:50,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们要带你走
You need to come with us.

615
00:53:52,120 --> 00:53:55,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们仍然无法恢复王宫的屏障
We are still unable to restore the palace shields.

616
00:53:55,310 --> 00:53:57,040
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}重炮也无法瞄准黑暗精灵
Our artillery cannot detect them,

617
00:53:57,040 --> 00:53:59,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}就连海姆达尔也看不到他们
even Heimdall cannot see them.

618
00:54:02,020 --> 00:54:03,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我的陛下
My king,

619
00:54:04,040 --> 00:54:05,820
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们失去了防御能力
we're all but defenseless.

620
00:54:08,460 --> 00:54:10,100
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你们把她抓起来了
She's your prisoner now?

621
00:54:12,330 --> 00:54:13,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}都退下
Leave us.

622
00:54:22,680 --> 00:54:24,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不想和你争论什么
I do not wish to fight with you.

623
00:54:25,390 --> 00:54:27,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我也不想和你争论
Nor I with you.

624
00:54:27,310 --> 00:54:29,220
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}但我想去找玛勒基斯
But I intended to pursue Malekith.

625
00:54:29,260 --> 00:54:31,000
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}以太在我们手里
We possess the Aether.

626
00:54:31,240 --> 00:54:32,720
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯会来找我们
Malekith will come to us.

627
00:54:32,720 --> 00:54:34,670
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}是啊 他会把我们全都毁灭
Yes, and he will destroy us.

628
00:54:34,670 --> 00:54:37,090
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}要知道 你高估了那些家伙的能量
You overestimate the power of these creatures.

629
00:54:37,090 --> 00:54:39,410
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不 我只是不想看到这儿血流成河
No, I value our people's lives.

630
00:54:39,410 --> 00:54:41,020
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我要带简去黑暗世界
I'll take Jane to the Dark World,

631
00:54:41,020 --> 00:54:43,350
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}让敌人远离阿萨神域
and draw the enemies away from Asgard.

632
00:54:43,530 --> 00:54:45,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}只要玛勒基斯从简体内取出以太粒子
When Malekith pulls the Aether from Jane,

633
00:54:45,590 --> 00:54:47,920
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}它的效力就会大打折扣
it would be exposed and vulnerable.

634
00:54:47,920 --> 00:54:50,080
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我能把他们彻底毁灭
And I would destroy it and him.

635
00:54:51,610 --> 00:54:52,970
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果你失手
If you fail,

636
00:54:53,690 --> 00:54:56,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那件武器就有可能落到我们敌人手中
you risk this weapon falling into the hands of our enemie.

637
00:54:56,620 --> 00:54:59,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果束手待毙 危险将会更大
The risk is far greater if we do nothing.

638
00:54:59,320 --> 00:55:01,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他的舰队可能已经在我们上方
His ships could be over our heads right now,

639
00:55:01,250 --> 00:55:02,480
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}只是我们无法察觉
we would never even know.

640
00:55:02,700 --> 00:55:04,020
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果他胆敢来犯
If and when he comes,

641
00:55:04,170 --> 00:55:07,760
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我会叫他有来无回 死无葬身之地
his men will fall on ten thousand Asgardian blades.

642
00:55:07,760 --> 00:55:09,570
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那样我们不知道要死多少人
And how many our men should fall on theirs?

643
00:55:09,570 --> 00:55:11,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}死多少我也在所不惜
As many as I need it.

644
00:55:20,620 --> 00:55:21,890
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们要战斗
We will fight

645
00:55:24,780 --> 00:55:26,680
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}战斗到最后一个人
till the last Asgardian breath,

646
00:55:28,060 --> 00:55:30,190
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}战斗到流尽最后一滴血
till the last drop of Asgardian blood.

647
00:55:33,340 --> 00:55:36,450
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}那你和玛勒基斯有什么区别
Then how are you different from Malekith?

648
00:55:39,520 --> 00:55:41,820
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们的区别就是 我赢了
The different, my son, is that I will win.

649
00:55:56,290 --> 00:55:57,770
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}现在简也不回电话
Jane isn't calling me back.

650
00:55:57,900 --> 00:55:59,390
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}艾瑞克也不回电话
Erik isn't calling me Back.

651
00:55:59,420 --> 00:56:01,170
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}该死的神盾局也不回电话
Stupid S.H.I.E.L.D isn't calling me back.

652
00:56:01,170 --> 00:56:02,210
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}什么神盾局
What's S.H.I.E.L.D?

653
00:56:02,210 --> 00:56:03,030
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不告诉你
It's a secret.

654
00:56:03,210 --> 00:56:05,430
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}嗨 艾瑞克 我是达茜 还是我
Hi, Erik, it's Darcy again.

655
00:56:05,690 --> 00:56:06,800
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}索尔回来过
Thor came back,

656
00:56:06,840 --> 00:56:08,230
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他把简带走了
he took Jane to Asgard.

657
00:56:08,230 --> 00:56:12,160
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}还有 我 现在有点不知所措
And I'm not sure what I'm suppose to do.

658
00:56:12,210 --> 00:56:13,960
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不过 我们遗漏了很多内容
Something else went missing this week,

659
00:56:13,960 --> 00:56:17,000
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}本周发生了天体物理学家艾瑞克·萨维德博士
when astrophysicist Dr. Erik Selvig

660
00:56:17,050 --> 00:56:19,690
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}在巨石阵裸奔的事情 他因卷入了外星人
notable for his involvement in the alien invasion

661
00:56:19,690 --> 00:56:20,680
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}入侵纽约事件
of New York.

662
00:56:20,870 --> 00:56:24,480
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}- 而闻名- 达茜 你应该看看这个
- Stripped nude... - Darcy, you really need to look at this.

663
00:56:25,020 --> 00:56:26,340
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你的朋友艾瑞克
Your friend Erik,

664
00:56:26,480 --> 00:56:27,930
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他姓什么来着
what was his last name again?

665
00:56:29,150 --> 00:56:32,570
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}赤身裸体朝参观历史遗迹的人们大喊大叫
...and began shouting at visitors to the historic site.

666
00:56:32,580 --> 00:56:35,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}随后他被带回到当地警局
He was later taken into police custody

667
00:56:35,240 --> 00:56:37,260
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}以便能进行精神评估
for psychiatric evaluation.

668
00:56:37,660 --> 00:56:39,960
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}目前警方仍然拒绝
The police is still refusing to confirm...

669
00:56:50,240 --> 00:56:52,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你没有出席战前会议
You were not at Odin's war council.

670
00:56:52,590 --> 00:56:55,270
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你的父王已经下令完全封闭彩虹桥
The Bifrost is closed by your father's orders.

671
00:56:55,270 --> 00:56:57,300
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}禁止任何人通行
No one was to come, or to go.

672
00:56:59,610 --> 00:57:02,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我甚至看不到我们的敌人
We face an enemy that is invisible even to me,

673
00:57:02,310 --> 00:57:06,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}要我这样的守护者 能有什么用呢
what use is a guardian such as that.

674
00:57:07,210 --> 00:57:09,860
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯不会善罢甘休 你知道的
Malekith will return. You know this.

675
00:57:12,960 --> 00:57:14,210
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我需要帮助
I need your help.

676
00:57:14,810 --> 00:57:16,880
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不能违背国王的旨意
I cannot overrule my king's wishes.

677
00:57:17,510 --> 00:57:18,620
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}即便是为了你
Not even for you.

678
00:57:18,620 --> 00:57:19,980
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不是那个意思
I'm not asking you to.

679
00:57:20,230 --> 00:57:22,920
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}九大国度需要一个无比强大的众神之父
The realms need their All-father strong and unchallenged,

680
00:57:22,920 --> 00:57:24,470
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}无论他称职与否
whether he is or not.

681
00:57:25,420 --> 00:57:27,110
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可是他受到了蒙蔽
But he's binded Heimdall,

682
00:57:27,750 --> 00:57:29,250
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}因为仇恨和痛苦
by hatred and by grief.

683
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:30,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们都是一样
As are we all.

684
00:57:30,180 --> 00:57:31,960
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不过我还算清醒
I see clearly enough.

685
00:57:32,430 --> 00:57:34,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们面临巨大的危险
The risks are to great.

686
00:57:34,070 --> 00:57:36,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们今后的道路布满了荆棘
Everything we do from here on is a risk.

687
00:57:36,680 --> 00:57:38,260
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}而且别无选择
There is no other way.

688
00:57:42,690 --> 00:57:44,230
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你想让我做什么
What do you require of me.

689
00:57:44,950 --> 00:57:48,160
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我想让你做的就是违背王命 抗旨不尊
What I'm about to ask you is treason of the highest order.

690
00:57:48,760 --> 00:57:50,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}成功了我们会被流放
Success will bring us exile,

691
00:57:50,590 --> 00:57:52,540
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}失败了我们将人头落地
and failure shall mean our death.

692
00:57:55,590 --> 00:57:58,150
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯知道以太在这里
Malekith knew the Aether was here.

693
00:57:58,240 --> 00:57:59,760
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他能感知它的力量
He can sense its power.

694
00:58:00,130 --> 00:58:02,590
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}如果我们再不行动 他肯定会卷土重来
If we do nothing, he'll come for it again,

695
00:58:02,590 --> 00:58:05,880
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}到那时阿萨神域将会万劫不复
but this time, lay waste to all of Asgard.

696
00:58:07,800 --> 00:58:09,700
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们必须把简转移出去
We must move Jane off world.

697
00:58:10,040 --> 00:58:11,310
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}彩虹桥已经完全关闭了
The Bifrost has been shut down,

698
00:58:11,310 --> 00:58:13,420
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}宇宙魔方锁在仓库里
and the Tesseract locked away in the vault.

699
00:58:13,890 --> 00:58:15,830
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}阿萨神域还有一条出路
There are other path off Asgard,

700
00:58:16,190 --> 00:58:17,830
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}只有很少的人知道
ways known only to a few.

701
00:58:17,960 --> 00:58:19,540
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}只有一人知道
One actually.

702
00:58:22,080 --> 00:58:22,720
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}不
No.

703
00:58:28,080 --> 00:58:29,320
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}索尔
Thor.

704
00:58:29,930 --> 00:58:31,430
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}过了这么久
After all this time,

705
00:58:31,430 --> 00:58:33,120
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你终于想到来看看我了
now you come to visit me,

706
00:58:35,190 --> 00:58:36,190
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}为什么
why?

707
00:58:37,970 --> 00:58:39,470
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}幸灾乐祸
Have you come to gloat?

708
00:58:40,390 --> 00:58:41,010
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}还是嘲弄我
To mock?

709
00:58:41,010 --> 00:58:42,240
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}已经够了
Loki enough.

710
00:58:43,070 --> 00:58:44,560
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}别再掩饰自己了
No more illusions.

711
00:58:52,010 --> 00:58:53,510
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这就是真相 兄弟
Now you see me brother.

712
00:59:02,780 --> 00:59:03,980
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}弗丽嘉痛苦吗
Did she suffer?

713
00:59:04,240 --> 00:59:06,610
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不是来跟你分享痛苦的
I did not come here to share our grief.

714
00:59:07,210 --> 00:59:10,290
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我来是想为你提供一个悔过自新的机会
Instead I offer you the chance of a far richer sacrament.

715
00:59:11,560 --> 00:59:12,550
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}请说
Go on.

716
00:59:13,020 --> 00:59:15,370
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我知道你和我一样热衷于复仇
I know you seek vengeance as much as I do.

717
00:59:16,000 --> 00:59:18,650
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你帮我离开阿萨神域 我就给你机会
You help me escape Asgard and I will grant it to you.

718
00:59:19,120 --> 00:59:20,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}去复仇
Vengeance.

719
00:59:20,700 --> 00:59:22,090
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}然后再回到这里
And afterwards this cell.

720
00:59:29,800 --> 00:59:33,990
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你一定是走投无路了 才会想到来找我
You must be truely desperate to come to me for help.

721
00:59:36,370 --> 00:59:37,840
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你怎么知道可以相信我
What makes you think you can trust me.

722
00:59:37,840 --> 00:59:38,910
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我不相信
I don't.

723
00:59:41,060 --> 00:59:42,020
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}妈妈相信
Mother did.

724
00:59:43,330 --> 00:59:45,950
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我想说在我们以往的交锋中
But you should know that when we fought each other in the past,

725
00:59:46,900 --> 00:59:48,210
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我的确对你抱有一丝希望
I did so with a glimpse of hope

726
00:59:48,220 --> 00:59:50,350
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}因为你毕竟是我的兄弟
that my brother was still in there somewhere.

727
00:59:51,720 --> 00:59:54,070
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}可那种希望现在已经不存在了
That hope is no longer exist to protect you.

728
00:59:55,100 --> 00:59:57,090
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}你若敢背叛我 我就杀了你
You betray me, and I will kill you.

729
01:00:04,100 --> 01:00:05,240
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}我们何时开始
When do we start?

730
01:00:05,800 --> 01:00:07,230
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}他会出卖你
He will betray you.

731
01:00:07,520 --> 01:00:08,460
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}让他试试
He will try.

732
01:00:13,250 --> 01:00:15,180
{\pos(98,255)\fscx50}这可不像你的作风 兄弟
This is so unlike you, brother.

733
01:00:16,000 --> 01:00:17,540
