1334
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:55,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我作为仁慈的神 去中土世界
I went down to Midgard to rule the people of Earth

1335
00:04:55,730 --> 00:04:57,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}统治地球的子民
as a benevolent god,

1336
00:04:58,710 --> 00:04:59,910
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}就像你一样
just like you.

1337
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们并不是神
We are not gods.

1338
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:06,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们也有生老病死 和人类一样
We are born, we live, we die, just as humans do.

1339
00:05:07,610 --> 00:05:09,460
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但我们有五千年的寿命
Give or take five thousand years.

1340
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:14,130
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}今天这一切都源于洛基对王位的追求
All this because Loki desires a throne.

1341
00:05:14,130 --> 00:05:15,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那是我应有的权力
It's my birthright!

1342
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,780
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你的权力
Your birthright

1343
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,650
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是死亡
was to die...

1344
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是幼年夭折
as a child!

1345
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,350
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}被丢弃在冰冷的岩石上
Cast out onto a frozen rock.

1346
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:28,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果我没有收留你
If I had not taken you in

1347
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你就不会像现在这样恨我了
you would not be here now to hate me.

1348
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:33,800
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果我不该活着的话 那就请你慈悲为怀
If I am for the axe, then for mercy's sake,

1349
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}赐我一死
just swing it.

1350
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,700
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我并非不喜欢这次谈话
It's not that I don't love our little talks,

1351
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:39,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我只是
it's just...

1352
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我的确不喜欢
I don't love them.

1353
00:05:43,620 --> 00:05:45,950
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果不是弗丽嘉你早就一命呜呼了
Frigga is the only reason you are still alive

1354
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你再也见不到她
and you will never see her again.

1355
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:51,340
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我要让你一辈子待在地牢里
You will spend the rest of your days in the dungeons.

1356
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:56,700
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那么索尔呢
And what of Thor?

1357
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:01,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你要让那个白痴去当国王 让我把牢底坐穿
You'll make that witless oaf king while I rot in chains?

1358
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:04,940
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}索尔必须去收拾你留下的烂摊子
Thor must strive to undo the damage you have done,

1359
00:06:05,730 --> 00:06:08,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他得让九大国度恢复秩序
he will bring order to the nine Realms and then,

1360
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:11,440
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是的 他会是国王
yes, he will be king.

1361
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}其实我已经完全掌握局势了
I've got this completely under control!

1362
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:03,180
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}难怪这儿如此热闹
Is that why everything's on fire!

1363
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不用客气
You're welcome.

1364
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:52,020
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}看你的了
All yours.

1365
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你好
Hello.

1366
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:20,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我接受你的投降
I accept your surrender.

1367
00:08:33,170 --> 00:08:34,030
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}还有人吗
Anyone else?

1368
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}看来下次我们得先拿个大的开刀
Perhaps next time we should start with the big one.

1369
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们接下来干什么
Where do we go next?

1370
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:09,770
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}九大国度即将迎来和平
Hogun, the peace is nearly won across the Nine Realms.

1371
00:09:11,070 --> 00:09:11,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你应该留下
You should stay here

1372
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:13,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}和你的人民在一起
be with your people where your heart is,

1373
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,090
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}暂时不回阿萨
Asgard can wait.

1374
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}真是太谢谢你了
You have my thanks.

1375
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,650
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也要谢谢你
As you have mine.

1376
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}海姆达尔 可以了吗
Heimdall, when you're ready.

1377
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:13,900
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}瓦纳海姆安全了吗
Is Vanaheim secure?

1378
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不亚于诺恩海姆和瑞亚
As are Nornheim and Ria.

1379
00:10:16,410 --> 00:10:18,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}您要是御驾亲征 会更早结束
Though our work would have gone more quickly with you at the fore.

1380
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,770
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}看来你把我当成马屁股了
You must think I'm a piece of bread

1381
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}最近没事就想拍一拍
that needs to be buttered so heavily.

1382
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我可没那个意思
That was not my intent.

1383
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,790
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}自从彩虹桥遭到破坏以来
For the first time since Bifrost was destroyed,

1384
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:30,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}九大国度首次回归和平
the Nine Realms are at peace.

1385
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:33,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他们会记住我们的强大
They're well reminded of our strength

1386
00:10:33,450 --> 00:10:37,480
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你赢得了他们的尊敬 还有我的感谢
and you have earned their respect and my gratitude.

1387
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:39,250
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}谢谢
Thank you.

1388
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:44,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}一切都恢复了秩序 除了你那无法平静的内心
Nothing out of order except your confused and distracted heart.

1389
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:47,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这跟简·福斯特无关 父王
This isn't about Jane Foster, father.

1390
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:49,380
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}人类的生命转瞬即逝
Human lives are fleeting, they're nothing.

1391
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:52,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你应该珍惜自己的大好前程
You'd be better served by what lies in front of you.

1392
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:56,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我并非以众神之父的身份和你说话
I'm telling you this not as the All-father,

1393
00:10:56,410 --> 00:10:57,720
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我是你父亲
but as your father.

1394
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,670
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你长大了 到了接掌王位的时候了
You are ready, the time has come for you to take the throne.

1395
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}去享受和庆祝你的胜利
Embrace and celebrate what you've won.

1396
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,140
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}到将士们中间
Join your warriors,

1397
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:07,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}开怀畅饮 跟他们彻夜狂欢
eat and drink, revel in their celebration.

1398
00:11:08,010 --> 00:11:10,100
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}至少也该做做样子吧
At least pretend to enjoy yourself.

1399
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,500
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}再来一杯
Another.

1400
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:15,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}有些狂欢至少应该持续几个星期
There was a time when you would celebrate for weeks.

1401
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:19,950
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我记得你曾醉心于庆祝哈罗金战役
I remember you celebrated the Battle of Harokin

1402
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}以至于你差点又去打第二次
so much that you nearly started the second.

1403
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,030
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是啊 第一次那么开心
Well, the first was so much fun.

1404
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:33,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}陪我喝一杯
Take a drink with me.

1405
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:36,530
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你父王今晚不会再给你安排新任务了吧
Surely the All-father could have no further task for you tonight.

1406
00:12:36,530 --> 00:12:38,580
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可是 我给自己安排了任务
No, this is one I set myself.

1407
00:12:40,810 --> 00:12:43,480
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我不是不知道你每晚都在玩消失
It does not go unnoticed that you disappear each night.

1408
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:45,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们有九大国度
There are Nine Realms,

1409
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:49,470
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}未来的国王可不能只盯着其中一个
the future king of Asgard must focus on more than one.

1410
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:58,500
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}谢谢你的骁勇善战和坦诚相见 希芙小姐
I thank you for your sword and for your counsel, good Lady Sif.

1411
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你好
Hi.

1412
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你好
Hi.

1413
00:13:23,830 --> 00:13:25,130
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你有什么心事吗
So what's the story with you?

1414
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:27,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}为什么要有心事 我没心事
Why does there have to be a story, there's no story.

1415
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,910
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}要知道 自从我们见面以后
You spent the first ten minutes of our date

1416
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,650
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你一直在研究菜谱 可那上面只有三种选择
hiding behind a menu that has three choices on it.

1417
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:34,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}无非是鸡肉 蔬菜和鱼
It's either chicken, vegetarian or fish, Jane.

1418
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}所以我认为你有心事
I think there's a story

1419
00:13:36,850 --> 00:13:40,330
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}而且一定是和某个男人有关系
and I'm thinking the story involves a guy?

1420
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,330
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这可说来话长了
It's complicated.

1421
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:43,690
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他还在这儿吗
Is he still around?

1422
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:45,180
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不 他
No, he...

1423
00:13:46,310 --> 00:13:47,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他离开了
went away.

1424
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,330
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我能理解
I've been there.

1425
00:13:48,810 --> 00:13:51,260
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}分手是非常痛苦的 对吗
The going away. It's hard, isn't it?

1426
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:54,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我曾经追过一个女孩 后来她去了纽约工作
I was seeing a woman and uh...she took a job in New York,

1427
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:57,040
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们还是输给了距离
eventually the distance killed it.

1428
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}其实 其实她
And...and the fact that she uh...

1429
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她一直和其他男人上床
she kept sleeping with other dudes.

1430
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:02,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 不 - 哦 无数人
- No! - Oh, so many.

1431
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:06,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}嗨 呃 能给我们来点红酒吗
Hi. Um...could we get some wine please?

1432
00:14:06,730 --> 00:14:07,690
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}当然 我也想喝
Sure, I'd love some.

1433
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:09,900
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}理查德 这位是达茜
Richard, this is Darcy.

1434
00:14:10,380 --> 00:14:11,420
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你来干什么
What are you doing here?

1435
00:14:13,610 --> 00:14:15,260
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}噢 你好
Oh, hello.

1436
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:19,210
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}听着 我刚才去你的实验室就是你妈妈家上班
So, I show up to work at the lab/your mom's house,

1437
00:14:19,210 --> 00:14:22,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我本来以为你会 穿着睡衣转来转去
fully expecting you to be moping around in your pajamas

1438
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:26,150
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}一边吃冰淇淋 一边想念 那个人
eating ice cream obsessing about... you know who...

1439
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:29,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可是你没有 你穿了淑女装
But you're not! You're wearing lady clothes,

1440
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:31,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}还洗了澡 对吗 闻着挺香
you even showered, didn't you? You smell good.

1441
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,370
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你到底有什么事
Is there a point to all this,

1442
00:14:32,370 --> 00:14:34,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我说你总不会平白无故地来找我吧
because there really needs to be a point to all this.

1443
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,060
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}对
Right.

1444
00:14:36,330 --> 00:14:38,700
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}记得那些你已经失去兴趣的科学仪器吗
You know all that scientific equipment you don't look at anymore?

1445
00:14:39,430 --> 00:14:41,190
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}也许你应该再看上一眼
You might wanna start looking at it again.

1446
00:14:41,410 --> 00:14:43,500
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}为了它才大老远跑来的
This is the reason we came all the way out here.

1447
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:44,670
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它出故障了
It's malfunctioning.

1448
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也这么说
That's what I said.

1449
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:48,710
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也这么做
That's what I did!

1450
00:14:48,710 --> 00:14:50,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我以为你处理事情会科学点
I thought you'd do something a little more scientific.

1451
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,500
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 我想问题不大 - 是啊
- I'm sure it's nothing. - Yeah, it's...

1452
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:53,850
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}恐怕没那么简单
It doesn't look like nothing.

1453
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:56,660
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它的读数像语无伦次的艾瑞克
Kind of looks like the readings that Erik was rambling about.

1454
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:59,690
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们的朋友艾瑞克 有点走火入魔
Our friend Erik, kind of went banana-balls.

1455
00:14:59,690 --> 00:15:00,570
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他对他没兴趣
He's not interested.

1456
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:01,870
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 我也没兴趣 - 我有兴趣
 - I'm not interested. - I'm interested.

