I think I'm gonna have the sea bass.

1462
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:19,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}鲈鱼 好吧 鲈鱼好吃
Sea bass. Yeah, sea bass is good.

1463
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}鲈鱼 鲈鱼 鲈鱼 鲈鱼
Sea bass, sea bass, sea bass, sea bass,

1464
00:15:22,830 --> 00:15:27,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}鲈鱼 鲈鱼 鲈鱼 鲈鱼 鲈鱼
sea bass, sea bass, sea bass...sea bass. Sea bass...

1465
00:15:29,050 --> 00:15:30,600
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 鲈鱼 - 简
- Sea bass. - Jane,

1466
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,900
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}别再念叨鲈鱼了 好吗
maybe you should stop saying "sea bass"

1467
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:34,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}去找你的朋友吧
and go after your friend.

1468
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我真的很开心
This was so fun.

1469
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:39,200
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}好吧 下面轮到我念叨鲈鱼了
You know, I'll just stay here and say "Sea bass" alone.

1470
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,310
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我恨死你了
And I hate you.

1471
00:15:48,660 --> 00:15:50,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}怎么了 我说他很可爱
