1487
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:33,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}现在我正在巨石阵现场
I'm here at Stonehenge,

1488
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:36,640
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}为大家报道今天发生的新闻事件
for what has been an interesting unfolding of events today.

1489
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:37,970
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}上午11点刚过
The police were called to the scene

1490
00:16:37,970 --> 00:16:39,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}警察便接到电话赶到这里
shortly after 11 a.m. this morning,

1491
00:16:39,830 --> 00:16:43,350
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}一位看似很正常的步行者来到附近
after a seemingly harmless rambler approached the area

1492
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:45,310
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}随后 他决定脱光衣服
then, decided to strip naked

1493
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:49,050
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他随身携带的科学仪器把周围的旅行者吓得不轻
and effectively terrorize tourists there with scientific equipment

1494
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:51,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但是他却扬言要拯救他们
while shouting that he was trying to save them.

1495
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:54,580
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}随后确认该名男子正是著名天文物理学家
The man later identified as noted astrophysicist

1496
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:55,750
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}艾瑞克·萨维格博士
Dr. Erik Selvig

1497
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:58,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}目前他已被带回警局 接受讯问
has been called in for questioning by police.

1498
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:02,660
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}快点 太激动人心了
Come on, this is exciting!

1499
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你瞧 实习生多兴奋
Look, the intern is excited.

1500
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:06,030
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}伊安
"Ian".

1501
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:07,710
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你需要相位计吗
Do you want the phase meter?

1502
00:17:07,710 --> 00:17:09,420
