- No. - Bring the phase meter.

1503
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}像烤面包机的那个
The toaster-looking thing.

1504
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:13,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}好 我知道什么是相位计
Yeah. I know what the phase meter is.

1505
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:24,140
