How do I change the ringtone on this thing?

1506
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,090
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}拥有三个学位的天体物理学家
An astrophysicist with three degrees

1507
00:17:26,090 --> 00:17:28,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不应该问这种问题
should be able to change her own ringtone.

1508
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}为什么打电话
Why are you calling me?

1509
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:30,040
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}因为我不想喊叫
I didn't want to shout.

1510
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}实习生说在这边
Intern says it's this way.

1511
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:33,360
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}伊安 我 我叫伊安
"Ian". My name is Ian.

1512
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:51,150
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我可不想为了科学献身
I am not getting stabbed in the name of science.

1513
00:17:51,150 --> 00:17:52,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}有话好说 我们是美国人
It's okay, we're Americans!

1514
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这样他们就喜欢我们了
Is that supposed to make them like us?

1515
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,350
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他们能让它消失
They'll make it go away.

1516
00:17:58,420 --> 00:17:59,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}噢 几个孩子
Oh, they're kids.

1517
00:18:00,490 --> 00:18:01,870
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你们是警察吗
Are you the police?

1518
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:06,020
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不 我们是科学家 至少我是
No, we're scientists. Well, I am.

1519
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:07,950
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 谢谢 - 我们刚刚发现
- Thanks. - We just found it.

1520
00:18:10,620 --> 00:18:11,760
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}能让我看看吗
Can you show us?

1521
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:39,950
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}好像不太对劲儿
That doesn't seem right.

1522
00:18:57,890 --> 00:18:58,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它去哪儿了
Where'd it go?

1523
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:13,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}真是
That's...

1524
00:19:14,010 --> 00:19:15,210
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}真是难以置信
that's incredible.

1525
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:29,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}怎么回事
What happened?

1526
00:19:30,450 --> 00:19:33,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它们有时候回来 有时候不回来
Sometimes they come back, sometimes they don't.

1527
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:39,100
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也想扔点什么 简 把你的鞋给我
I want to throw something. Jane, give me your shoe.

1528
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:43,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我还从没见过这样的读值
I haven't seen readings like this since...

1529
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,440
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}除了在
since...

1530
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,460
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}新墨西哥
New Mexico?

1531
00:19:51,010 --> 00:19:52,340
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}什么都不要动
Don't touch anything!

1532
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:56,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}把鞋给我
Give me your shoe.

1533
00:20:18,390 --> 00:20:20,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那是车钥匙吗
Were those the car keys?

1534
00:20:58,810 --> 00:20:59,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}达茜
Darcy!

1535
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:22,530
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你来晚了
You're late.

1536
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:27,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}欢乐有时候比战争更令人难以忍受
Merriment can sometimes be a heavier burden than battle.

1537
00:23:27,410 --> 00:23:29,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是你的欢乐方式有问题
Then you're doing one of them incorrectly.

1538
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:31,340
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可能吧
Perhaps.

1539
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,860
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}各星球情况如何
How fare the stars?

1540
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:35,630
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}依然在闪烁
Still shining.

1541
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:39,200
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}从这里 我可以看到九大国度和数万亿的生灵
From here I can see nine realms and ten trillion souls.

1542
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:46,250
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}记得我跟你讲过天体聚合吗
Do you recall what I told you of the Convergence?

1543
00:23:46,250 --> 00:23:49,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}记得 所有国度排成一列
Yes, the alignment of the worlds.

1544
00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:51,330
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}即将出现 对吗
It approaches, doesn't it?

1545
00:23:51,850 --> 00:23:53,610
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}从我开始守望以来
The universe hasn't seen this marvel

1546
00:23:53,610 --> 00:23:55,720
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}还从未见过这样的宇宙奇观
since before my watch began.

1547
00:23:56,850 --> 00:23:59,800
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}知道它的人很少 见过的人更少
Few can sense it, even fewer can see it.

1548
00:24:01,850 --> 00:24:03,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}尽管它存在一定的风险
But while its effects can be dangerous,

1549
00:24:04,970 --> 00:24:07,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可的确美不胜收
it is truly beautiful.

1550
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:10,100
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我看不出来
I see nothing.

1551
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:14,090
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}也许它并不是你追求的那种美
Or perhaps that is not the beauty you seek.

1552
00:24:20,010 --> 00:24:20,790
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她怎么样了
How is she?

1553
00:24:21,470 --> 00:24:23,350
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你的人类女友很聪明
She's quite clever, your mortal.

1554
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:24,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}尽管她还不了解天体聚合
She doesn't know it yet,

1555
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,720
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但她正在进行研究
but she studies the Convergence as well.

1556
00:24:27,620 --> 00:24:28,320
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}甚至
Even...

1557
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:31,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}怎么
What?

1558
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:36,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她不见了
I can't see her.

1559
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:17,640
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简
Jane!

1560
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,440
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你到底去哪儿了
Where the hell were you?

1561
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:22,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}别告诉我你已经报警了
Tell me you didn't call the police!

1562
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:23,250
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那我还能干什么
What was I supposed to do?

1563
00:25:23,250 --> 00:25:24,320
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不应该报警
Not call the police!

1564
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,120
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你吓坏我了
I was freaking out.

1565
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你报警 就会惊动政府
You call the cops, they tell the Feds,

1566
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:28,490
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}接着 神盾局的人会从四面八方赶来
the next thing you know we have S.H.I.E.L.D crawling all over,

1567
00:25:28,490 --> 00:25:29,630
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}把这儿变成51区
"Area 51-ing" the place.

1568
00:25:29,630 --> 00:25:32,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 简 - 我们发现了稳定的重力异常
- Jane! - We had a stable gratification anomaly,

1569
00:25:32,410 --> 00:25:33,840
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}而且可以随意研究
We had unimpeded access.

1570
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:35,710
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们的竞争对手只有几个孩子
Our only competition was ten years old!

1571
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:38,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简 你失踪了整整五个小时
Jane, you were gone for five hours!

1572
00:25:38,530 --> 00:25:39,230
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}什么
What?

1573
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:47,620
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}奇怪
That's weird.

1574
00:26:09,810 --> 00:26:10,610
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}老一套
Typical.

1575
00:26:12,020 --> 00:26:12,800
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简
Jane.

1576
00:26:15,630 --> 00:26:18,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}对不起 我只是确认你是不是真的
Sorry. I just needed to make sure you were real,

1577
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}今天一整天都怪怪的
it's been a very strange day.

1578
00:26:19,980 --> 00:26:21,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我是真的 简
Well, I am. Jane what...

1579
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,530
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你去哪儿了
Where were you?!

1580
00:26:23,530 --> 00:26:24,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你去哪儿了
Where were you?

1581
00:26:25,330 --> 00:26:26,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}海姆达尔看不到你
Heimdall could not see you.

1582
00:26:26,900 --> 00:26:28,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我就在我们分手的地方
I was right here where you left me.

1583
00:26:28,820 --> 00:26:31,040
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我一直苦苦等待 一边等一边哭
I was waiting and then I was crying

1584
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,720
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}后来又出去找你
and then I went out looking for you.

1585
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:33,860
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你说过你会回来
You said you were coming back.

1586
00:26:33,860 --> 00:26:36,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}知道 知道 可是彩虹桥被破坏了
I know, I know, but the Bifrost was destroyed.

1587
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:38,570
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}要知道九大国度乱作一团
The Nine Realms erupted into chaos,

1588
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:41,050
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}烽烟四起 掠夺者趁火打劫
wars were raging, marauders were pillaging.

1589
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:43,180
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我必须先结束动乱
I had to put an end to the slaughter.

1590
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:48,040
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果真是这样 那还说得过去
As excuses go, it's not terrible.

1591
00:26:48,450 --> 00:26:51,670
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可我在电视上看到你了 你 你在纽约
But I saw you on TV, you were...you were in New York!

1592
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:54,710
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简 我去那儿是为了保护人类不受上界的侵扰
Jane, I fought to protect you from the dangers of my world,

1593
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:57,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可是我错了 我是个傻瓜
but I was wrong, I was a fool.

1594
00:26:59,570 --> 00:27:02,760
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但我相信是命运 让我们走到一起
But I believe that fate brought us together.

1595
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:07,080
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简 我不知道你去了哪儿 做了什么
Jane, I don't know where you were or what happened,

1596
00:27:07,090 --> 00:27:08,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可是我知道
but I do know this.

1597
00:27:09,210 --> 00:27:09,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}什么
What?

1598
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:12,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我知道
I know...

1599
00:27:13,650 --> 00:27:14,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你知道
You do?

