{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}知道什么
Do what?

1601
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:18,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}什么
What?

1602
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:20,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}嗨
Hi.

1603
00:27:22,320 --> 00:27:23,370
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这是你干的
Is this you?

1604
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,880
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}呃 我们正在讨论问题
Uh...we're kind of in the middle of something here.

1605
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:33,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}嗯 可是我们肯定会被抓起来
Um...I'm pretty sure we are getting arrested.

1606
00:27:33,070 --> 00:27:34,040
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}别忘了刚才说的
Hold that thought.

1607
00:27:35,420 --> 00:27:36,850
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}瞧瞧你
Look at you!

1608
00:27:36,850 --> 00:27:40,170
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}四肢还是那么发达 天上怎么样
Still all muscly and everything. How's space?

1609
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:41,700
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}挺好的
Space is fine.

1610
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:44,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}对不起
Excuse me?

1611
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:45,800
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}- 你是简·福斯特 - 我是
- Are you Jane Foster? - Yes.

1612
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:46,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你认识他吗
Do you know this man?

1613
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:49,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他是我的实习生
He's my intern.

1614
00:27:50,420 --> 00:27:51,660
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}实习生的实习生
My intern's intern.

1615
00:27:51,660 --> 00:27:52,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这是私人领地
This is private property

1616
00:27:52,730 --> 00:27:54,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你们涉嫌非法入侵
and you're trespassing, the lot of you.

1617
00:27:54,270 --> 00:27:55,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}跟我走一趟
You'll have to come with me.

1618
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:01,900
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简
Jane!

1619
00:28:02,630 --> 00:28:03,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简
Jane?

1620
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:04,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}索尔
Thor.

1621
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:06,170
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你还好吗
You alright?

1622
00:28:06,410 --> 00:28:08,090
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}发生了什么事
What just happened?

1623
00:28:08,090 --> 00:28:10,570
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}把你的手放在头上 往后退
Place your hands on your heads, step back!

1624
00:28:10,570 --> 00:28:11,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这位女士身体不适
This woman is unwell.

1625
00:28:11,890 --> 00:28:13,060
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她很危险
She's dangerous.

1626
00:28:13,650 --> 00:28:14,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也一样
So am I.

1627
00:28:16,090 --> 00:28:18,440
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}请求特警现场支援
Requesting armed response officers to the scene.

1628
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}抓紧我
Hold on to me.

1629
00:28:19,430 --> 00:28:20,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你想干嘛
What are you doing?

1630
00:28:28,530 --> 00:28:30,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我的 天呐
Holy shit!

1631
00:28:58,050 --> 00:28:59,540
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们又来了一次
We have to do that again.

1632
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,240
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你好
Hi.

1633
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:05,790
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}阿萨神域欢迎你
Welcome to Asgard.

1634
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,060
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那是什么
What's that?

1635
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:00,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}安静
Be still.

1636
00:30:07,890 --> 00:30:09,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这是非地球物质 见过吗
This is not of Earth, what is it?

1637
00:30:10,860 --> 00:30:11,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}从没见过
We do not know.

1638
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:16,340
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不过她体内翻腾的能量 足以令她致命
But she will not survive the amount of energy surging within her.

1639
00:30:22,860 --> 00:30:25,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那是量子场发生器 对吗
That's a quantum field generator, isn't it?

1640
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:26,660
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这是灵魂锻造炉
It's a Soul Forge.

1641
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:30,490
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那么灵魂锻造炉可以使分子能量进行迁移 对吗
Does a Soul Forge transfer molecular energy from one place to another?

1642
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是的
Yes.

1643
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:36,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}还是量子场发生器
Quantum field generator.

1644
00:30:37,470 --> 00:30:40,340
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我的话就像耳旁风 对你完全不起作用吗
My words are mere noises to you that you ignore them completely?

1645
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:41,600
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她生病了
She's ill.

1646
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,770
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她是凡人
She is mortal.

1647
00:30:43,630 --> 00:30:45,360
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}凡人当然会生病
Illness is their defining trait.

1648
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:47,060
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我带她来 是因为我们可以帮她
I brought her here because we can help her.

1649
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:49,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她不能进我们阿萨神域的殿堂
She does not belong here in Asgard

1650
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:52,610
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}就像有些菜不能上台面一样
anymore than a goat belongs at a banquet table.

1651
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:53,980
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他怎么
Did he just...?

1652
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:56,260
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你以为你是谁啊
Who do you think you are?

1653
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:58,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我是奥丁 众神之王
I'm Odin. King of Asgard.

1654
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}九大国度的保护者
Protector of the Nine Realms.

1655
00:31:02,740 --> 00:31:03,250
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}哦 我
Oh. Well, I'm...

1656
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:06,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我知道你是谁 简·福斯特
I know very well who you are, Jane Foster.

1657
00:31:07,270 --> 00:31:08,820
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你跟你父亲说过我
You told your dad about me?

1658
00:31:09,550 --> 00:31:10,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她体内存在某种物质 父王
Something is within her, father,

1659
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我从未见过的物质
something I have not seen before.

1660
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:14,650
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}人类世界有自己的治疗师 叫医生
Her world has its healers. They are called "doctors."

1661
00:31:14,650 --> 00:31:15,620
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}让医生处理吧
Let them deal with it.

1662
00:31:15,910 --> 00:31:17,750
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}卫兵 马上送她回地球
Guards, take her back to Midgard.

1663
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,480
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不 别
No, I wouldn't...

1664
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:23,620
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}碰她
...touch her.

1665
00:31:23,980 --> 00:31:25,190
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简 你没事吧
Jane, are you alright?

1666
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这不可能
It's impossible.

1667
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:35,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她体内的物质 在保护她
The infection, it's defending her.

1668
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,270
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不
No,

1669
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,620
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它在保护自己
it's defending itself.

1670
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:42,050
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}跟我来
Come with me.

1671
00:31:42,820 --> 00:31:46,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}有一些宇宙形成前残留的物质
There are relics that predate the universe itself.

1672
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:50,530
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}她体内的东西 似乎是其中的一种
What lies within her appears to be one of them.

1673
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:53,760
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}九大国度并非一成不变
The Nine Realms are not eternal.

1674
00:31:54,410 --> 00:31:56,990
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它们有黎明 当然也有黄昏
They had a dawn as they will have a dusk.

1675
00:31:58,100 --> 00:32:00,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}在黎明之前 黑暗势力
But before that dawn the dark forces,

1676
00:32:00,430 --> 00:32:04,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}也就是黑暗精灵 一统天下
the Dark Elves, reigned absolute

1677
00:32:04,220 --> 00:32:05,930
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}独霸一方
and unchallenged.

1678
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}起源于无边黑暗的
"Born of eternal night,

1679
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:11,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}黑暗精灵要把光偷走
the Dark Elves comes to steal away your light."

1680
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:15,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我知道那些故事 小时候妈妈给我讲过
They were these stories mother told them to us as children.

1681
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他们的首领 玛勒基斯
Their leader, Malekith

1682
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,120
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}利用黑暗制造了一种武器
made a weapon out of that darkness,

1683
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:20,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}叫做以太
and it was called the Aether.

1684
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:23,760
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}其它的残留物通常很像石头
While the other relics often appeared as stones,

1685
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:26,660
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但以太是液体 并且不断变化
the Aether is fluid and everchanging.

1686
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:29,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它把各种物质转化成黑暗物质
It changes matter into dark matter,

1687
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,350
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它寻找寄居的宿主
it seeks out to host bodies,

1688
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:33,870
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}从宿主的生命力中吸取能量
drawing strength from their life force.

1689
00:32:34,250 --> 00:32:37,320
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯企图通过以太的力量
Malekith sought to use the Aether's power

1690
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:41,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}使宇宙重新回归黑暗
to return the universe to one of darkness.

1691
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:44,630
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但是 经过不屈不挠的浴血奋战
But after eternities of blood shed,

1692
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:47,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我的父王波尔 最终获得胜利
my father Bor, finally triumphed,

1693
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:52,210
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}因此赢得了持续数千年的和平
ushering in the peace that lasted thousands of years.

1694
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:54,150
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他怎么取胜的
What happened?

1695
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他消灭了他们
He killed them all.

1696
00:32:57,390 --> 00:32:58,780
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你肯定吗
Are you certain?

1697
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,620
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}据说以太也同时被消灭了
The Aether was said to have been destroyed with them

1698
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:03,020
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可如今再度献身
and yet here it is.

1699
00:33:04,390 --> 00:33:06,320
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}黑暗精灵的确消亡了
The Dark Elves are dead.

1700
00:33:07,610 --> 00:33:10,140
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你的书中有没有提到 怎么排出它们
Does your book happen to mention how to get it out of me?

1701
00:33:11,010 --> 00:33:14,430
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}没有 没有涉及
No, it does not.

1702
00:34:38,390 --> 00:34:41,320
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}让我们负责看管俘虏 未免太大材小用了
Acting as caretakers to these scoundrels is beneath us.

1703
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:42,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}噢 没错
Oh, please.

1704
00:34:42,750 --> 00:34:44,800
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你的身材的确够大 我的朋友
If they were beneath you my rotund friend,

1705
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}能把人压死
they'd all be dead.

1706
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:01,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}排好队
Keep in line.

1707
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:03,110
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}走快点
Move it!

1708
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:06,920
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}奥丁不断地为我提供新的朋友
Odin continues to bring me new friends.

1709
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,900
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}真的很体贴
How thoughtful.

1710
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:12,630
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我送来的书你不感兴趣是吗
The books I sent, do they not interest you?

1711
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:17,500
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你想让我后半辈子当书虫吗 读书
Is that how I'm to wile away eternity, reading?

1712
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:20,740
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我已经竭尽全力让你过得舒适一些了 洛基
I've done everything in my power to make you comfortable, Loki.

1713
00:35:20,740 --> 00:35:21,860
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}是吗
Have you?

1714
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:24,830
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}奥丁是否也这么想
Does Odin share your concern?

1715
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,420
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}还有索尔
Does Thor?

1716
00:35:27,810 --> 00:35:31,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}让他们日夜为我操心 我还真有点过意不去
It must be so inconvenient them asking after me day and night.

1717
00:35:31,410 --> 00:35:34,940
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你走到今天这一步 完全都是你咎由自取
You know full well it was your actions that brought you here.

1718
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:36,280
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}咎由自取
My actions.

1719
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:38,230
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我只不过是揭穿了那个
I was merely giving truth to the lie

1720
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:40,120
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}欺骗了我一生的谎言而已
that I've been fed my entire life,

1721
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,810
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}说什么我生而为王
that I was born to be a king.

1722
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,850
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}当国王
A king?

1723
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:45,870
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}真正的国王勇于承认错误
A true king admits his faults.

1724
00:35:45,870 --> 00:35:47,410
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你在地球上残害了多少生命
What of the lives you took on Earth?

1725
00:35:47,410 --> 00:35:50,680
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}跟伟大的奥丁杀的人相比 那点人根本不值一提
A mere handful compared to the number Odin has taken himself.

1726
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:51,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你父亲
Your father...

1727
00:35:51,890 --> 00:35:53,650
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}他不是我的父亲
He's not my father!

1728
00:35:56,700 --> 00:35:58,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也不是你母亲吗
Then am I not your mother?

1729
00:36:03,970 --> 00:36:05,150
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你也不是
You're not.

1730
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:14,700
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}除了你自己 你好像已经把所有的人都看透了
You're always so perceptive about everyone but yourself.

1731
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:32,440
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你去地球找我 是因为我遇到了麻烦
When you came for me, you knew I was in trouble.

1732
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:36,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}海姆达尔看不到你了 你不在地球上
When Heimdall had lost sight of you, you were no longer on Earth.

1733
00:36:36,420 --> 00:36:37,910
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}那怎么可能呢
Well, how's that possible?

1734
00:36:37,910 --> 00:36:39,780
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我认为你在 可你不在
I believe you were and you weren't.

1735
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:42,490
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}九大国度运行于宇宙生命之树
The Nine Realms travel within Yggdrasil,

1736
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:46,080
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它们围绕中庭旋转 犹如地球围绕太阳
orbiting Midgard in much the way your planet orbits the sun.

1737
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:50,630
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}每过五千年 它们就会呈直线排列
And every five thousand years the worlds align perfectly,

1738
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:52,450
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们称之为天体聚合
and we call this the Convergence.

1739
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:58,250
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}在这段时间 各国边界会出现混淆
During this time the boarders between worlds become blurred.

1740
00:36:59,540 --> 00:37:01,880
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}可能你已经发现了一些端倪
It's possible you found one of these points.

1741
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:06,120
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}幸好这情况还会改变
We are lucky that it remained open.

1742
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:10,030
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}天体聚合过后 直列现象结束
Once the worlds pass out of alignment,

1743
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:14,210
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}混淆情况就会消失
the connection is lost.

1744
00:37:27,270 --> 00:37:29,730
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我非常喜欢你的表述方式
I liked the way you explained things.

1745
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:33,260
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我会有什么事吗
What's gonna happen to me?

1746
00:37:33,450 --> 00:37:34,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我会想办法救你 简
I'll find a way to save you, Jane.

1747
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你父王说 根本
Your father said there was...

1748
00:37:36,010 --> 00:37:38,420
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我父王并非无所不知
My father doesn't know everything.

1749
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:40,670
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这话可别让他听到
Don't let him hear you say that.

1750
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:44,150
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}简·福斯特 请拜见弗丽嘉
Jane Foster, please meet Frigga,

1751
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:46,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}阿萨神域王后 我母亲
Queen of Asgard, my mother.

1752
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:49,390
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你好
Hi.

1753
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:40,760
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}快
Move!

1754
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,560
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}都去地牢
To the dungeons!

1755
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:30,890
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}快点
Come on!

1756
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:56,600
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我觉得你应该走左侧的楼梯
You might want to take the stairs to the left.

1757
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:08,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}监狱出事了
The prisons.

1758
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:09,840
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}洛基
Loki.

1759
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:12,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}去吧 我会照顾好她
Go, I will look after her.

1760
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}看来他们坐牢久了有点情绪
It is as if they resented being imprisoned.

1761
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:32,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}有些家伙就是不识好歹
There's no pleasing some creatures.

