{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我是玛勒基斯
I am Malekith.

1787
00:47:23,450 --> 00:47:25,520
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}来取回属于我的东西
And I would have what is mine.

1788
00:47:56,700 --> 00:47:59,200
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你拿了我的东西 孩子
You have taken something, child.

1789
