everything is connected,

1803
00:52:15,810 --> 00:52:19,640
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}包括九大国度 九大国度会互相穿行
all nine realms. All nine realms are passing through each other,

1804
00:52:19,640 --> 00:52:22,120
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}重力 光线 甚至物质
and gravity, light, and even matter

1805
00:52:22,120 --> 00:52:24,460
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}都会彼此碰撞 混合
