1806
00:52:26,940 --> 00:52:30,400
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果我们发生这种情况 结果将是毁灭性的
But if this happens to us now, the result could be cataclysmic.

1807
00:52:31,190 --> 00:52:33,310
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我发明的尖峰重力测试仪
My gravimetric-spikes can stablize

1808
00:52:33,560 --> 00:52:36,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}能够稳定天体聚合焦点
the focus point of the Convergance.

1809
00:52:36,190 --> 00:52:38,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}这样一来 九大国度
This time, the Alignment

1810
00:52:38,560 --> 00:52:41,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}和其它星体队列就不会碰到我们
and all the other worlds would just pass us by.

1811
00:52:41,690 --> 00:52:43,010
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它很完美
It's beautiful.

1812
00:52:44,710 --> 00:52:45,950
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}也很简单
Simple.

1813
00:52:45,950 --> 00:52:47,290
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}有问题吗
Any questions?

1814
