{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们失去了防御能力
we're all but defenseless.

1822
00:54:08,460 --> 00:54:10,100
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你们把她抓起来了
She's your prisoner now?

1823
00:54:12,330 --> 00:54:13,510
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}都退下
Leave us.

1824
00:54:22,680 --> 00:54:24,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我不想和你争论什么
I do not wish to fight with you.

1825
00:54:25,390 --> 00:54:27,310
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我也不想和你争论
Nor I with you.

1826
00:54:27,310 --> 00:54:29,220
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}但我想去找玛勒基斯
But I intended to pursue Malekith.

1827
00:54:29,260 --> 00:54:31,000
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}以太在我们手里
We possess the Aether.

1828
00:54:31,240 --> 00:54:32,720
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯会来找我们
Malekith will come to us.

1829
