{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}它的效力就会大打折扣
it would be exposed and vulnerable.

1836
00:54:47,920 --> 00:54:50,080
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我能把他们彻底毁灭
And I would destroy it and him.

1837
00:54:51,610 --> 00:54:52,970
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}如果你失手
If you fail,

1838
