1870
00:56:37,660 --> 00:56:39,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}目前警方仍然拒绝
The police is still refusing to confirm...

1871
00:56:50,240 --> 00:56:52,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你没有出席战前会议
You were not at Odin's war council.

1872
