{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你的父王已经下令完全封闭彩虹桥
The Bifrost is closed by your father's orders.

1873
00:56:55,270 --> 00:56:57,300
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}禁止任何人通行
No one was to come, or to go.

1874
00:56:59,610 --> 00:57:02,310
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我甚至看不到我们的敌人
We face an enemy that is invisible even to me,

1875
00:57:02,310 --> 00:57:06,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}要我这样的守护者 能有什么用呢
what use is a guardian such as that.

1876
00:57:07,210 --> 00:57:09,860
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}玛勒基斯不会善罢甘休 你知道的
Malekith will return. You know this.

1877
00:57:12,960 --> 00:57:14,210
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我需要帮助
I need your help.

