{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}因为仇恨和痛苦
by hatred and by grief.

1885
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:30,180
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们都是一样
As are we all.

1886
00:57:30,180 --> 00:57:31,960
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}不过我还算清醒
I see clearly enough.

1887
00:57:32,430 --> 00:57:34,070
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们面临巨大的危险
The risks are to great.

1888
00:57:34,070 --> 00:57:36,550
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我们今后的道路布满了荆棘
Everything we do from here on is a risk.

1889
00:57:36,680 --> 00:57:38,260
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}而且别无选择
There is no other way.

1890
00:57:42,690 --> 00:57:44,230
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}你想让我做什么
What do you require of me.

1891
00:57:44,950 --> 00:57:48,160
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}我想让你做的就是违背王命 抗旨不尊
What I'm about to ask you is treason of the highest order.

1892
00:57:48,760 --> 00:57:50,590
{\pos(286,255)\fscx50}成功了我们会被流放
Success will bring us exile,

1893
